{"tid":1519681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日狗鐵如果一早封站係好事，如果佢開頭冇封，都唔好信同依賴","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:44:13.000Z","uid":149250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b5809cb8f2d769a4385dc1cd7f627f5a67b24a","tid":1519681,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"狗鐵唔可信就係人都知架啦，我想提提各位巴絲，如果你到時想走，或者危險要走，入地鐵站前或者今晚好諗定，如果狗鐵再狗啲，等你走哂落去先封站停車落閘放狗，咁就仆街架啦，如果冇辦法落到去，又真係走唔到，請組埋同路人，打番出去，或者打落路軌，你平時唔勇唔緊要，你走投無路都唔勇，就玩完架啦，你打輸都係食咁多，但係贏左你就冇事。最後，唔該包實自己，戴手套，出去返屋企都小心啲，兜小小路，大鳩捕開始左架啦，唔好比位人入呀<br />\n<br />\n聽日見<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"8d0be9bcb5fb4d8cf993d06cb9504f81abb4e105","tid":1519681,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0n8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=5d85102f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0n8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=34854583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: smal